Cyberpunk style: A massive holographic data stream flowing through a neon-lit urban canyon at night, with glowing XML-like angular brackets and ampersand symbols fragmenting and reassembling as they cascade through the air like digital rain. The stream splits into three distinct parallel ribbons of cyan, magenta, and electric purple light, each carrying chunks of abstract data particles. In the foreground, a silhouetted figure stands on a platform observing the data flow through augmented reality goggles, surrounded by floating translucent panels showing waveform patterns. The architecture features towering black monolithic servers with pulsing circuit patterns, reflecting off wet streets below. Steam rises from vents, catching the chromatic glow of the streaming data overhead.
